query.result:
94 He left her there, pregnant and alone;
95 such a sin condemns him to such torment;
96 and vengeance is also taken for Medea.

97 With him goes whoever deceives in such a way;
98 and let this suffice to know
99 of the first valley and of those it engulfs.
